1. Macro architecture: subsystems
Think of the system as 6 subsystems:

Data & Indexing Subsystem – how raw PDFs and your rotations catalog become queryable.

Retrieval Subsystem – hybrid search + reranking over both corpus and catalog.

Reasoning Subsystem – LLM routing, safety, Hindi explainer, and optimization logic.

Serving Subsystem – FastAPI gateway, auth, rate limiting, multi‑tenant support.

Evaluation & CI/CD Subsystem – golden sets, automated RAG eval, and quality gates.

Observability Subsystem – logs, traces, dashboards, and drift/hallucination monitoring.

You already did (3) pretty well; we’ll thicken (1), (2), (5), (6).

